name: Serie Tribute: 15 - Catwoman
description:
This new series has a collectible card format. It will make a tribute tour about superheroes and villains. A new creative venture of Roboto Inc. for its great collectors. Prototypes designed by Norma Xelda Jara. Let's have fun! 

First appearance: Batman No. 1; (spring 1940); DC Comics
In Batman vol. 1 #35 (1946) Catwoman starts wearing her classic costume, which would accompany her for many years: hood, long skirt and cape, with purple and green tones.
